---
/**
 * SVG Icon Sprite
 *
 * Contains all dental-specific icons used in premium cards.
 * Include this component once in your layout.
 * Reference icons using: <use href="#icon-{name}" />
 *
 * Available icons:
 * - cleaning, whitening, implants, cosmetic, emergency
 * - checkup, crown, braces, extraction, filling
 * - root-canal, dentures, pediatric, orthodontics
